OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776510170
OL,3,CSomerset teacher says motability
OL,4,Cchanges will be 'devastating'
OL,6,FA wheelchair user from Somerset has
OL,7,Ftold ITV News that changes to a
OL,8,Fdriving scheme for disabled people
OL,9,Fwill affect her freedom and ability to
OL,10,Fwork.
OL,12,FKay Millar, from Frome, is one of more
OL,13,Fthan 800,000 people in the UK who use
OL,14,Fthe Motability scheme to lease a car,
OL,15,Fwhich is paid for through her
OL,16,Fgovernment-funded mobility allowance.
OL,18,FThe 29-year-old, who is a teacher by
OL,19,Fprofession, said she is "devastated"
OL,20,Fthat the rules to access the scheme
OL,21,Fare set to become stricter.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
