FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776510170
OL,3,CSomerset teacher says motability
OL,4,Cchanges will be 'devastating'
OL,6,FFrom July, the Motability Scheme will
OL,7,Fhalve the standard annual mileage
OL,8,Fallowance for most customers from
OL,9,F20,000 miles to 10,000 miles per year.
OL,11,FDrivers who go over 30,000 miles in
OL,12,Fthree years will have to pay 25p per
OL,13,Fextra mile. Previously, the excess was
OL,14,F5p per extra mile.
OL,16,FMs Millar said that in the two years
OL,17,Fthat she's been part of the scheme,
OL,18,Fshe has already covered 43,000 miles.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776510170
OL,3,CSomerset teacher says motability
OL,4,Cchanges will be 'devastating'
OL,6,F"With the new scheme, I'd already be
OL,7,Fabout #3,200 over the budget," she
OL,8,Fexplained.
OL,10,F"I use my car for my surfing career
OL,11,Fand my basketball career. I also use
OL,12,Fit for treatment in Surrey, in Bristol
OL,13,Fand further down south in Salisbury.
OL,14,FWithout that treatment, I can't
OL,15,Fsurvive. Without my athlete status, I
OL,16,Fhave no quality of life.
OL,18,F"This is another restriction they've
OL,19,Fplaced on us that's going to force us
OL,20,Fback into our homes."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776510170
OL,3,CSomerset teacher says motability
OL,4,Cchanges will be 'devastating'
OL,6,FShe added: "10,000 miles is enough
OL,7,Fwhen you can get the bus, train, or
OL,8,Fwalk, but when it's a mobility
OL,9,Fcomponent, those miles add up really
OL,10,Fquickly.
OL,12,F"It's not that people are using it to
OL,13,Fgo off on holiday. It's seriously
OL,14,Fgetting from A to B."
OL,16,FEmily, a motability user from Cornwall
OL,17,Fwho uses her vehicle to attend
OL,18,Fvolunteering sessions at Newquay
OL,19,FOrchard, said the changes to scheme
OL,20,Fhave left her feeling "anxious."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776510170
OL,3,CSomerset teacher says motability
OL,4,Cchanges will be 'devastating'
OL,6,F"It's making me sad. It's very
OL,7,Fdiscriminating," she added.
OL,9,FHer dad, Paul, said the scheme enables
OL,10,FEmily "to live the life that she wants
OL,11,Fto live."
OL,13,F"To take that away from her, or to
OL,14,Fpenalise her financially with a fee
OL,15,Fthat she cannot afford to pay, means
OL,16,Fthat she can no longer live the life
OL,17,Fthat she wants to live and that is not
OL,18,Fright," he said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776510170
OL,3,CSomerset teacher says motability
OL,4,Cchanges will be 'devastating'
OL,6,FDisability support group Bridges for
OL,7,FChange said the changes were
OL,8,Fintroduced without proper consultation
OL,9,For assessment of their impact on
OL,10,Fdrivers with disabilities.
OL,12,FSandy Lawrence, Bridges for Change
OL,13,FCIC, said: "I hadn't heard of any
OL,14,Fconsultation about it. So I knew
OL,15,Fnothing. The first thing I knew about
OL,16,Fit was after receiving an email from
OL,17,Fthe Chief Executive of Motability."
OL,19,F"It's going to affect the lives of so
OL,20,Fmany children, young people and adults
OL,21,Fwith disabilities."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776510170
OL,3,CSomerset teacher says motability
OL,4,Cchanges will be 'devastating'
OL,6,FIn a statement, a spokesperson for
OL,7,FMotability Operations said changing
OL,8,Fthe mileage allowance of future leases
OL,9,F"will lower insurance and maintenance
OL,10,Fcosts and increase the vehicle's
OL,11,Fresale cost, which reduces the cost of
OL,12,Fa lease."
OL,14,F"We will be introducing an exceptions
OL,15,Fprocess for very limited situations,"
OL,16,Fthey added.
OL,18,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,19,Four political experts are across all
OL,20,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,21,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
